title: The Three Stooges Dopey Dicks (1950) Colorized Enhanced

sources.title: The Three Stooges Dopey Dicks (1950) Colorized Enhanced
sources.description: "Dopey Dicks" (1950) The Stooges, working as janitors, are mistaken for detectives and tasked with rescuing a distressed woman. Their bumbling investigation leads them to a creepy mansion where a mad scientist is building robot men. Chaos, slapstick, and Stooge-style mischief follow at every turn. Nonstop laughs ensue as the Stooges fumble their way through danger and disaster. Colorized then zapped with digital enhancements, as God intended...
